Examples for Telos queries
--------------------------

Add the models Employee_Classes, Employee_Instances, and
Employee_Queries. Then display the instances of QueryClass
in your usage environment. Some of them are explained in the user manual,
the others should be self-explanatory.
You can edit them or ask them directly. With the X11-UE you will get the
answer in a dedicated answer window. 


